Class SemanticAnalysis<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.myorb.math.expressions.tree.SemanticAnalysis<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of expression values

    public class SemanticAnalysis<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    apply type information to expression tree. adjust tree node for sub-expressions identified by semantic symbol data.

    Michael Druckman
